# Scam Hunters Journey Map (with Artifact References)

This document maps the user experience across all primary entry points into the Scam Hunters ecosystem. Each node is linked to specific artifacts (see `artifact_index.md`) and includes user intent, content block, and expected behavior.

---

## 🗺️ Mermaid Diagram (Journey Flow)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Lands on ScamHunters Entry Point] --> B{Entry Channel}

    B -->|Funnel Ad or Link| C[funnel_intro_mat]
    B -->|Direct Visit| D[home_main]
    B -->|Facebook Post| E[FB Page / Story]
    B -->|Google Search| G[storefront_main]

    %% Funnel Flow
    C --> hero_intro_grandma["Reads Personal Story - hero_intro_grandma"]
    hero_intro_grandma --> C2[Clicks 'Get the Mat']
    C2 --> C3[Checkout Page]
    C3 --> confirmation_shared
    confirmation_shared --> C5[Suggested Gear or Joke]
    C5 --> G

    %% Homepage flow
    D --> D1[Reads Mission / Intro CTA]
    D1 -->|Explore Gear| G
    D1 -->|Join Posse| C

    %% FB Flow
    E --> E1[Clicks on Shared Post or Button]
    E1 -->|Product| G
    E1 -->|Joke| J[jokes_laugh_lasso]
    E1 -->|Join Funnel| C

    %% Store Path
    G --> G1[Browses Products]
    G1 --> G2[Clicks Hoodie / Mat / Case]
    G2 --> G3[Store Checkout]
    G3 --> confirmation_shared

    %% Joke Path
    J --> J1[Clicks on Joke Product]
    J1 -->|Punchline in Description| J2[Engages, Shares, Buys Gear]
    J2 --> G

    %% Final Outcomes
    G -->|Leaves| Z[Done for Now]
    G -->|Follows FB| FB[Joins Community]
```

---

## 🧩 Artifact Mapping (Summary)

| Page                  | Artifact                                                                              | Notes                              |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `home_main`           | `cta_explore_gear`, `cta_join_posse`, `featured_gear_row`, `footer_unified_v1`       | Entry overview and routing         |
| `funnel_intro_mat`    | `hero_intro_grandma`, `footer_unified_v1`                                            | Story-driven entrypoint            |
| `confirmation_shared` | `cta_explore_gear`, `joke_teaser_card`, `footer_unified_v1`                          | Shared endpoint for store + funnel |
| `storefront_main`     | `announcement_banner_v1`, `featured_gear_row`, `cta_join_posse`, `footer_unified_v1` | Browsable product hub              |
| `jokes_laugh_lasso`   | `joke_card_001`, `footer_unified_v1`                                                 | Collection of humorous decoys      |

